<reference id="repo-layout-and-variants" xml:lang="en-US">
  <title>Repository Layout and Build Variants</title>
  <shortdesc>Recommended real-world repository structure for DITA projects and how to use DITAVAL filtering to produce audience/platform build variants.</shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <author>Extense LLC</author>
